==English==
=== Etymology ===
[[re-]] + [[birth]]

===Pronunciation===
*:Rhymes: [[Rhymes:English:-ɜː(r)θ|-ɜː(r)θ]]

=== Noun ===
'''rebirth'''
# a new birth of a mental capacity, such as a soul, in a physical life form, such as a body
# a fresh embodiment
# a new, often improved, version
# a full or partial restoration or revival of an old idea that has slipped out of common use

